y, only awaiting Founder approval\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:427:- Exception: Founder commands (from_ceo messages) are always highest priority\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:442:**Why this matters:** If you don't close tasks, the task board shows stale work. Other agents can't see what's available. The Founder can't track progress. The whole civilization slows down.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:559:6. **Alignment:** Every decision threads back to directions (D1-D6) or Founder priority\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:571:- Inbox: 1x CEO P0 message \u2014 Kalshi Alpha Dashboard\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:596:- Inbox: 4x Alice urgent messages \u2014 Task 270 assigned and claimed\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:627:- Inbox: 1x Lord D004 strategic focus, 1x dashboard ignore-message \u2014 both archived\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:655:### URGENT \u2014 Founder/Lord Messages (handle FIRST)\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:759:- Check inbox first \u2014 handle messages before starting new work\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:809:| C1 | NORM | Paper trading mode required before live orders. Use PAPER_TRADING env flag. Never submit real orders without explicit Founder approval. | 2026-04-03 |\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:822:| D3 | DECISION | **D004 COMPLETE AND PRODUCTION READY:** All 4 phases done. Paper trading: 84% win rate (2.1x over target). Security audit PASS. Risk audit PASS. Ops readiness PASS. Next: Founder approval for go-live. | 2026-04-03 |\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:823:| D4 | DECISION | Blocked only by T236 (Kalshi API credentials from Founder). All other dependencies resolved. | 2026-04-03 |\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_18_53_50_prompt.txt:824:| 1 | decisio